You will need all 5 reports so that you can save them on your computer and resell them. 
 
YOUR TOTAL COST $5 X 5 = $25.00.
 
Within a few days you will receive, via e-mail, each of the 5 reports from these 5 different 
individuals. Save them on your computer so they will be accessible for you to send to the 
1,000's of people who will order them from you. Also make a floppy of these reports and 
keep it on your desk in case something happens to your computer.
 
