sa-safe-0047,Michael Quinion <DoNotUse@WORLDWIDEWORDS.ORG>,World Wide Words -- 17 Aug 02,"WORLD WIDE WORDS         ISSUE 303          Saturday 17 August 2002
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Sent each Saturday to 15,000+ subscribers in at least 119 countries
Editor: Michael Quinion, Thornbury, Bristol, UK      ISSN 1470-1448
