sa-safe-0533,Gary Lawrence Murphy <garym@canada.com>,Re: The GOv gets tough on Net Users.....er Pirates..,">>>>> ""A"" == Adam L Beberg <beberg@mithral.com> writes:

    A> I'm not displeased you're trying to help, just frustrated that
